doc.section:
Project Entity: { id, name, description, type: 'personal'|'shared', color, icon, ownerId, createdAt, updatedAt, memberCount, threadCount }
ProjectMember Entity: { projectId, userId, role: 'owner'|'editor'|'viewer', addedAt, addedBy }
Role Permission Matrix: Owner/Editor/Viewer × Permissions (view, create_thread, invite_member, etc.)
